node.text:
First in-depth look at the house we built in Montana. The house is 1248sq ft, 12’ walls, 6:12 roof, and overlooks our little lake.

Huge thanks to my amazing sponsor Ferguson Showrooms for providing the appliances, fixtures, and lighting.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Theron Humphrey on July 29, 2021. May be an image of indoor.

node.text:
Garage studio project update! Drywall is done, HVAC is done, kitchen cabinets are here…I’m ready for paint this week then trim out and I’m done! ⁣
⁣
It took months of waiting for the white tool chest and storage cabinets to come in stock but I’m glad I did, gonna be a tidy feeling space ✨

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Theron Humphrey on July 29, 2021. May be an image of indoor.

Cabin! Excited to get rolling on a bunch of cabin updates and announce my lovely sponsor for the project: @buildwithferguson ✨there’s a link in my bio with free cabin plans to inspire you own project + everything I’m using for mine.⁣
⁣
I’ve been ordering nearly everything off their website since my first project, years ago now, back in Nashville. I can whole heartily say I’m a fan and if you’re building or remodeling it’s worth check them out. ⁣
⁣
Best part is you don’t have to compromise on what you want/need (because they have everything) AND they literally show you what’s in stock AND it ships fast.⁣
⁣
Anyhow! It’s truly my fav and worth checking them out for your project. ⁣
⁣
More updates coming often!

node.text:
Sometimes still images feel like sweet reverence…it’s almost like they are tricking us into believing that we can step in the same river twice. But we all know you can’t, life is constantly changing. And this morning I’m OK with that. ⁣
⁣
I do know I was exactly where I was suppose to be last night. Sitting with friends in awe of Montana’s sky, of that summer light that broke through the storm clouds. ⁣
⁣
So is the only constant is change and we’re not promised tomorrow I figured I might as well spend my days creating and building things I love. So I’m gonna. And I hope you do too ✨
